45:38.096 --> 45:40.197
I'm sorry.

45:40.198 --> 45:41.200
I didn't mean to shout at you.

45:42.200 --> 45:44.300
[exhales]

45:44.301 --> 45:45.203
I just...

45:46.203 --> 45:49.472
I'm very upset about Matthew.

45:49.473 --> 45:51.377
Of course you are.

45:53.377 --> 45:55.278
The main thing is...

45:55.279 --> 45:57.014
