45:57.015 --> 45:58.317
to try to make it up to you.

46:00.317 --> 46:02.318
So in a few days,

46:02.319 --> 46:04.421
when you've had a chance to mourn,

46:04.422 --> 46:06.622
we can get coffee and discuss it.

46:06.623 --> 46:08.392
- I'd like that.
- Good.

46:08.393 --> 46:09.727
- I'd really like that.
- Good.

46:09.728 --> 46:11.394
OK, great. Now...

46:11.395 --> 46:13.195
- Dr. Lang?
- Yeah?

46:13.196 --> 46:15.502
I had a really funny dream a few nights ago.

46:18.502 --> 46:21.371
You and I, we lived in the countryside.

46:21.372 --> 46:23.741
In England.

46:24.741 --> 46:27.711
And we rode horses everywhere.

46:27.712 --> 46:29.646
And mine was a...

46:29.647 --> 46:32.615
Oh, he was a big white stallion

46:32.616 --> 46:36.385
